ee. Virtually, anyway. If that isn&#x2019;t enough to tempt you, they&#x2019;ll also be holding concerts by real celebrities like Fleetwood Mac&#x2019;s Bob Welch&#x2013;actually, his avatar Bob Welch Magic&#x2013;who will play at the launch party on Wednesday at 8pm CST. Tempting, but we&#x2019;ve misplaced our virtual lawn chairs.</p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}